4601056.title: List of Intel Core processors
4601056.extract: The following is a list of Intel Core processors. This includes Intel's original Core (Solo/Duo) mobile series based on the Enhanced Pentium M microarchitecture; as well as its Core 2– (Solo/Duo/Quad/Extreme), Core i3–, Core i5–, Core i7–, Core i9–, Core M– (m3/m5/m7/m9), Core 3–, Core 5–, Core 7–, and Core 9–branded processors.
